Package gov.sandia.geotess

Class GeoTessModelUtils.Point

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.sandia.geotess.GeoTessModelUtils.Point
  • Enclosing class:
    GeoTessModelUtils
    public static class GeoTessModelUtils.Point
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that represents a single point on the earth as both a unit vector and as an xy point projected using a Robinson projection. This class implements methods equals() and hashCode() making it suitable for storing in Set and Map objects.
